Ground floor fully self contained and partitioned office tenancy. Partitioning consists of reception, 4 offices, stationery and filing room and a small workshop area.

Located on Hulme Court, Myaree near the intersection of Leach Highway and North Lake Road.  Close proximity to Kwinana Freeway and Fremantle.

Area: 142sqm
Rent: $200/sqm per annum
Outgoings: Currently estimated at $53.32/sqm per annum for the 09/10 financial year
Available: September 2009

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please contact Kendall Forrest on 0439 700 717 or kendall.forrest@cbre.com.au

Fully partitioned and cabled Level 1 office tenancy available for lease at 16 Hulme Court, Myaree.

Modern tenancy with good natural light. Good quality partitioning throughout, two balcony areas, cabling, alarm system, and disabled
access.

The property is located just off Leach Highway near the intersection of North Lake Road and is within close proximity to Fremantle and the Kwinana Freeway.

Area: 440sqm
Rent: $250 / sqm
Outgoings: $53/sqm per annum

Ample parking available at no cost.

For further information please contact Luke Bray 0403 184 340

Office/warehouse with good exposure on a spacious stand-alone site in the heart of Myaree.

Features two street crossovers, 16 car bays front and side warehouse access with loading dock.

Extensive office and amenities within warehouse.

For Sale by Offers to Purchase closing Friday 5th December 2014 at 5.00pm WST (if not sold prior)

The key characteristics of the property include, but are not limited to:

- Located 11 kilometres* south-west of the Perth CBD
- Strategic land holding of 9,802sqm*
- Mixed Use zoning (Mixed Business frame)
- 75.44m* frontage to McCoy Street and frontage to Spargio Street and possible frontage to Blaike Street
- Improvements having a total area of 3,608sqm* NLA
- Being sold with a lease to Specialist Diagnostic Services Pty Ltd
- Low site coverage
- Secure covenant for over 5 years with options

*approx

The entire property is leased to Specialist Diagnostic Services Pty Ltd on a 10 year term commencing 1st May 2011 and expires on 30th April 2021 with two, five year options.
Primary Health Care is a guarantor to the lease.
Current net annual rental: $833,832.39 pa (review in May 2015)
Rent Reviews: annually to 3%
All normal outgoings are payable by the tenant.
NB: For full tenancy details and a copy of the lease please contact Geoff Fraser.

For further details contact Geoff Fraser on 0413 624 000.

Unique opportuninty to lease mezzanine offices suitable for 3 - 4 people.

3 carbays are available with the unit

Flexible lease terms.

Call Geoff Fraser on 0413624000 or 9320 0000
